doing a 2000’s party in 2023 is actually really a mind fuck for someone like me, who was actually around playing clubs since the early 2000’s. 

There is one part where you have to understand a majority of the crowd wasn’t even outside in the 2000’s, so by default they won’t know all the jams. 

The other side of me is like, nah f that, I’m gonna make it feel like the 2000’s because we’re doing this for one special day only… and they can shazam all these songs if they want to haha

I was happy this crowd was down, and they knew MOST of the songs I played 😂 I had like 800 songs in my folder and I only had 1.5 hours to dj so … couldn’t get to em all! 

Thx @djnaterioz @marcelanthony___ for having us 🫶 see y’all soon! @the.2000s.party btw all the DJs KILLED their sets!

And idk who won best 2000’s outfit. It was either @jaymeebaaby @djtasi or me 🤷🏻‍♂️ 😂
